title: Updated: Pixel 6 camera sample has not appeared, picture taken with Pixel 5
author: tom-bedford
article: Correction: Our original article contained inaccuracies and has been removed.
The original Facebook post by Zaheed Sabur was not taken down, and has since been updated to confirm the image in question "was shot on Pixel 5 and color graded by Zaheed Sabur".
Mr Sabur had in fact made no suggestion that his original Facebook post was referencing or demonstrating the Google Pixel 6.
